title: Ep. 16 - What should the title of this episode be? We can’t decide…
itunes:title: Ep. 16 - What should the title of this episode be? We can’t decide…
description: Do you have a hard time making decisions or are you one of the lucky few for whom decisiveness is built into your genetics? Can’t decide? Then this five minutes is for you. Wendy wants to shake some sense into those of us struggling with “decision fatigue.” Like, how hard can it be to pick out a bath mat?
